{"type": "article", "id": 23043, "title": "渐变果蔬汁", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-01T07:34:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 73, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607115617fWw02kp3SLF9iCOh.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">丰富绚丽的色彩已成为果蔬汁的卖点，这款哥伦比亚的果蔬汁也有漂亮的渐变色。Siegenthaler &amp; Co 使用了日出日落时的天空的色彩来表现自然无添加等传统的概念，在包装纸的下面，颜色渐变到果蔬汁本来的色彩。原有的混合果汁有几款都是相近的黄色，但在包装纸上使用了蓝或绿等不同的颜色，从而使 5 种果汁之间构成了很强的区别度。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115615yGwqP90xZTd7pSXM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115615AlcvndtGHzNfqg26.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115615R6eDa2QfbgOL0Fxw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071156160kcVv6NDoCJGBWql.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115616TfmFclw6gA2CkrV0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}